		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Hi manu, don&#8217;t know what i&#8217;m doing wrong. Tried this several times already candies come out nice at first but turns sticky and back to liquid 2-3 days after. Done everything from wrapping them in wax paper, sealed them in baggies, put them in the fridge. Our honey is around 21mc so i let the excess liquid evaporate first before letting it reach hard crack.</p>
