		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Yo, I think that you can just boil the sugar lemon and water, and then once it reaches to hard crack stage remove from heat, and once it cools down to 40C, immediately stir in the honey and pour into mold. This will keep all the benefits yayyyyy</p>
