			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time"><a class="comment-time-link" href="https://www.manusmenu.com/honey-hard-candy#comment-675707">February 21, 2017 at 12:46 pm</a></time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I&#8217;m using a silicone mold and the candy that touches the mold is not clear when removed.  Do you know what the problem could be?</p>
