	<li class="comment odd alt depth-2" id="comment-724552">
	<article id="article-comment-724552">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<img data-pin-nopin="nopin" alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/034dacd8cc83661470e235cd35d2adac928055e04d2829f1a25623d8a8f8eeed?s=48&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/034dacd8cc83661470e235cd35d2adac928055e04d2829f1a25623d8a8f8eeed?s=96&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/><span class="comment-author-name">Ryan Yeung, Hong Kong</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time"><a class="comment-time-link" href="https://www.manusmenu.com/honey-hard-candy#comment-724552">December 24, 2019 at 1:51 am</a></time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Maybe you haven&#8217;t cooked it to the right temperature.</p>
