<p><img data-pin-nopin="nopin" alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4a41527f0a8d01ea10bb8b59fb0e98847060aa3cf70cddb804139e4a333eae62?s=125&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4a41527f0a8d01ea10bb8b59fb0e98847060aa3cf70cddb804139e4a333eae62?s=250&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-125 photo' height='125' width='125' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/>Hi! I am Manu, the author of Manu's Menu. I was born and brought up in Italy and my blog can show you how to create authentic Italian food in your own home! <a class="pagelink" href="https://www.manusmenu.com/about/about-me">Read More…</a></p>
